<p class="subheading noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: 49px; line-height: 48.63999938964844px;">Spring Community Groups</span></p>
<p class="noPspace header subheading" dir="ltr"><span style="font-family: Helvetica, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Below is a list of Community Groups coming this Spring. Registration will begin the weekend of April 5-6.</span></p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">ONGOING</span></p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong><span style="line-height: 1.75;">GOING DEEPER</span></strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Join us for a new series called, Battlefield of the Mind. We&rsquo;ll take a look at the way our thinking impacts our ability to hear from God, receive his love and progress in our spiritual journey.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>MEN&rsquo;S ONGOING</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Join a community of men as they sharpen each other through prayer, studying God&rsquo;s word, and encouraging each other to put his plan into action in their daily lives.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>ALL YEAR JOURNEY</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Every year our community takes a 6-week community-wide journey together. We explore different topics that help us connect deeper to God&rsquo;s heart and to others. Come join us as we visit past journeys.</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">GROWTH</span></p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>THE GOD EXPERIMENT</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">If you are skeptical about God or you&rsquo;re wrestling with who God is, this group may help you sort through the unanswered questions.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>ALL FOR LOVE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Loving Jesus is more than a feeling- it&rsquo;s a transformative calling. Join us as we discover how God&rsquo;s love translates into a life full of purpose and mission.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>STORIES OF THE BIBLE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">This group looks at the major narrative themes of the bible in a way that makes an ancient text come to life.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>STORY FORMED LIFE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">SFL is a foundational, interactive training designed to expose and increase our faith in living God&rsquo;s story- not just knowing about it.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>UNDERSTANDING THE BIBLE</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">The Bible can be an overwhelming book to read. Learn a simple, step-by-step approach to understanding and applying what you&rsquo;re reading.</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr"><span style="text-decoration: underline;">LIFE STAGE</span></p>
<p class="sectionHeader noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>ADOPTION AND FOSTER PARENT GROUP</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">Monthly gathering for parents experiencing the joys and challenges of foster, adoptive and kinship parenting.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>DAVE RAMSEY&rsquo;S FINANCIAL PEACE UNIVERSITY</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">God calls us to be good managers of the resources he&rsquo;s given us, and that includes money. Learn what that looks like, and how to transform your approach to finances.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>MOMS</strong></p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr">For Moms seeking to understand how a relationship with God can impact how they engage with their family.</p>
<p class="noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>
<p class="subheading noPspace" dir="ltr"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>